<% content_for :title, "About Us — Kala Interiors & Decor" %>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" style="background: #0A1628; min-height: 60vh;">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600585154340-be6161a56a0c?w=1920&q=90&auto=format&fit=crop"
      alt="Kala Interiors studio"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      style="opacity: 0.18;"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,22,40,0.95) 0%, rgba(10,22,40,0.7) 100%);"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 w-full py-36">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #C9A84C; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Our Story</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="mb-5 leading-none" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem); color: #F8F7F4;">
        About <em style="color: #C9A84C;">Kala</em><br/>Interiors
      </h1>
      <p style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: rgba(248,247,244,0.55); max-width: 38rem; line-height: 1.8;">
        Born from a passion for beautiful spaces and skilled craftsmanship, Kala Interiors & Decor has been transforming homes across Telangana one room at a time.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOUNDER SECTION -->
<section class="py-24 lg:py-32" style="background: #F8F7F4;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="overflow-hidden" style="aspect-ratio: 4/5;">
          <img
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600210492486-724fe5c67fb0?w=800&q=85&auto=format&fit=crop"
            alt="Vivek Kumar Thodupunuri - MD, Kala Interiors"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <!-- Gold block -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-40 h-32 hidden lg:flex items-center justify-center" style="background: #C9A84C;">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; color: #0A1628;">8+</div>
            <div class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: rgba(10,22,40,0.7); font-size: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.15em;">Years of<br/>Excellence</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
          <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #C9A84C; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Meet the Founder</span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="mb-1 leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem); color: #0A1628;">
          Vivek Kumar Thodupunuri
        </h2>
        <div class="mb-6 text-sm" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #C9A84C; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.05em;">
          Managing Director, Kala Interiors & Decor
        </div>

        <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed text-sm" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(10,22,40,0.65);">
          Vivek Kumar Thodupunuri founded Kala Interiors & Decor with a singular vision: to make world-class interior design accessible to every homeowner in Telangana. With over 8 years of hands-on experience in the craft, Vivek has personally overseen hundreds of transformations across the state.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-5 leading-relaxed text-sm" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(10,22,40,0.65);">
          His philosophy is rooted in listening — understanding each client's unique lifestyle, taste, and aspirations before a single design is sketched. This client-first approach has built Kala Interiors into one of the most trusted interior design brands in the region.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed text-sm" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(10,22,40,0.65);">
          "Every home has a story. Our job is to help that story come alive through thoughtful design, quality materials, and craftsmanship that stands the test of time."
        </p>

        <div class="italic text-lg" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; color: #0A1628; font-weight: 400;">
          — Vivek Kumar Thodupunuri
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COMPANY STORY -->
<section class="py-24 lg:py-32" style="background: #0A1628;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #C9A84C; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Our Journey</span>
        <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="mb-6 leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); color: #F8F7F4;">
        The <em style="color: #C9A84C;">Kala</em> Story
      </h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed text-sm" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(248,247,244,0.55);">
        What began as a small carpentry and interior work operation has grown into one of Telangana's most comprehensive interior design firms. Driven by a relentless commitment to quality and client satisfaction, Kala Interiors expanded its service range year after year — from cupboards and ceilings to full home interior packages.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <div class="p-8" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-left: 2px solid #C9A84C;">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; color: #C9A84C;">2016</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg mb-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 400; color: #F8F7F4;">The Beginning</h3>
        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(248,247,244,0.5);">Kala Interiors started as a boutique carpentry unit in Hyderabad, specialising in custom plywood furniture and cupboards for residential clients.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-left: 2px solid #C9A84C;">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; color: #C9A84C;">2019</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg mb-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 400; color: #F8F7F4;">Service Expansion</h3>
        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(248,247,244,0.5);">Expanded into false ceiling, wallpapers, painting, and soft furnishings. Adopted 3D design visualization for all projects, dramatically improving client experience.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); border-left: 2px solid #C9A84C;">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; color: #C9A84C;">2024</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg mb-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 400; color: #F8F7F4;">Pan-Telangana</h3>
        <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(248,247,244,0.5);">Now serving all districts of Telangana with a full suite of 13 premium interior services and a portfolio of 500+ completed projects across the state.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="py-24 lg:py-32" style="background: #F8F7F4;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #C9A84C; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">What Drives Us</span>
        <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); color: #0A1628;">
        Our Core <em>Values</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <% [
        { icon: "M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z", title: "Quality First", desc: "We never compromise on materials or craftsmanship. Every joint, every finish, every installation is held to the highest standard." },
        { icon: "M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z", title: "Client-Centric", desc: "Your vision is our brief. We listen, adapt, and collaborate to ensure the final outcome exceeds your expectations." },
        { icon: "M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z", title: "On-Time Delivery", desc: "We respect your time and your home. Every project is managed with clear milestones and delivered on the agreed schedule." },
        { icon: "M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z", title: "Innovation", desc: "We stay ahead of design trends, continuously incorporating new materials, techniques, and technologies into our work." }
      ].each do |val| %>
        <div class="text-center p-8" style="background: white;">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5" style="background: rgba(201,168,76,0.1);">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="#C9A84C" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="<%= val[:icon] %>"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-3" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 400; color: #0A1628;"><%= val[:title] %></h3>
          <p class="text-xs leading-relaxed" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; color: rgba(10,22,40,0.6);"><%= val[:desc] %></p>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FULL WIDTH IMAGE -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="height: 65vh;">
  <img
    src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1618221195710-dd6b41faaea6?w=1920&q=90&auto=format&fit=crop"
    alt="Kala Interiors signature living space"
    class="w-full h-full object-cover"
  />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center" style="background: rgba(10,22,40,0.6);">
    <div class="text-center px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #C9A84C; letter-spacing: 0.2em;">Our Promise</span>
        <div class="w-10 h-px" style="background: #C9A84C;"></div>
      </div>
      <blockquote class="max-w-3xl" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem); color: #F8F7F4; font-style: italic; line-height: 1.5;">
        "We don't just decorate rooms. We create environments where families thrive, where memories are made, and where beauty is felt every single day."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="mt-6 text-sm" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #C9A84C; font-weight: 300;">
        — Vivek Kumar Thodupunuri, MD
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<section style="background: #C9A84C;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
      <% [["500+", "Projects Delivered"], ["8+", "Years Experience"], ["13", "Services Offered"], ["30+", "Districts Served"]].each do |stat| %>
        <div>
          <div class="text-5xl mb-1" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; color: #0A1628;"><%= stat[0] %></div>
          <div class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: rgba(10,22,40,0.65); font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 0.2em;"><%= stat[1] %></div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-20" style="background: #0A1628;">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="mb-4 leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem); color: #F8F7F4;">
      Let's Create Something <em style="color: #C9A84C;">Together</em>
    </h2>
    <p class="mb-10 max-w-md mx-auto" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: 0.9375rem; color: rgba(248,247,244,0.5);">
      Ready to transform your space? We'd love to hear about your project.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
      <%= link_to contact_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase transition-all hover:gap-5", style: "font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: #C9A84C; color: #0A1628; font-weight: 500;" do %>
        Get In Touch
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      <% end %>
      <%= link_to portfolio_path, class: "inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 text-xs tracking-widest uppercase transition-all hover:bg-white/10", style: "font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; color: #F8F7F4; border: 1px solid rgba(248,247,244,0.3);" do %>
        View Our Work
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
